label: trip
comment: Describes the trip the vehicle corresponding to this observation is making. SameAs: 'trip' field from GTFS Realtime message-TripUpdate (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-tripupdate)

label: vehicleDesc
comment: Describes the additional information of the vehicle corresponding to this observation. SameAs: 'vehicle' field from GTFS Realtime message-TripUpdate (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-tripupdate)

label: timestamp
comment: Describes the date-time at which the position of the vehicle corresponding to this observation was updated. SameAs: 'timestamp' field from GTFS Realtime message-TripUpdate (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-tripupdate)

label: stop_time_update
comment: Updated sorted stop sequence for the trip made by the vehicle corresponding to this observation, not to be considered if schedule_realtionship is "CANCELED". SameAs: 'stop_time_update' field from GTFS Realtime message-TripUpdate (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-tripupdate)
